{
  "chapter": {
    "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.8",
    "translationId": "lxxe",
    "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
    "chapterNumber": 8,
    "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8",
    "summary": "Source text for 1 Chronicles 8 in Brenton's English Septuagint."
  },
  "verses": [
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.8.1",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 1,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:1",
      "text": "Now Benjamin begot Bale his first-born, and Asbel his second son, Aara the third, Noa the fourth,",
      "paragraphStart": true
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.8.2",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 2,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:2",
      "text": "and Rapha the fifth.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.8.3",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 3,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:3",
      "text": "And the sons of Bale were, Adir, and Gera, and Abiud,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.8.4",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 4,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:4",
      "text": "and Abessue, and Noama, and Achia,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.8.5",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 5,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:5",
      "text": "and Gera, and Sephupham, and Uram.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.8.6",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 6,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:6",
      "text": "These were the sons of Aod: these are the heads of families to them that dwell in Gabee, and they removed them to Machanathi:",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.8.7",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 7,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:7",
      "text": "and Nooma, and Achia and Gera, he removed them, and he begot Aza, and Jachicho.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.8.8",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 8,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:8",
      "text": "And Saarin begot children in the plain of Moab, after that he had sent away Osin and Baada his wives.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.8.9",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 9,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:9",
      "text": "And he begot of his wife Ada, Jolab, and Sebia, and Misa, and Melchas,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.8.10",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 10,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:10",
      "text": "and Jebus, and Zabia, and Marma: these were heads of families.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.8.11",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 11,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:11",
      "text": "And of Osin he begot Abitol, and Alphaal.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.8.12",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 12,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:12",
      "text": "And the sons of Alphaal; Obed, Misaal, Semmer: he built Ona, and Lod, and its towns:",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.8.13",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 13,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:13",
      "text": "and Beria, and Sama; these were heads of families among the dwellers in Elam, and they drove out the inhabitants of Geth.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.8.14",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 14,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:14",
      "text": "And his brethren were Sosec, and Arimoth,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.8.15",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 15,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:15",
      "text": "and Zabadia, and Ored, and Eder,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.8.16",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 16,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:16",
      "text": "and Michael, and Jespha, and Joda, the sons of Beria:",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.8.17",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 17,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:17",
      "text": "and Zabadia, and Mosollam, and Azaki, and Abar,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.8.18",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 18,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:18",
      "text": "and Isamari, and Jexlias, and Jobab, the sons of Elphaal:",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.8.19",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 19,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:19",
      "text": "and Jakim, and Zachri, and Zabdi,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.8.20",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 20,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:20",
      "text": "and Elionai, and Salathi,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.8.21",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 21,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:21",
      "text": "and Elieli, and Adaia, and Baraia, and Samarath, sons of Samaith:",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.8.22",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 22,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:22",
      "text": "and Jesphan, and Obed, and Eliel,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.8.23",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 23,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:23",
      "text": "and Abdon, and Zechri, and Anan,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.8.24",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 24,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:24",
      "text": "and Anania, and Ambri, and Ælam, and Anathoth,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.8.25",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 25,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:25",
      "text": "and Jathin, and Jephadias, and Phanuel, the sons of Sosec:",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.8.26",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 26,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:26",
      "text": "and Samsari, and Saarias, and Gotholia,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.8.27",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 27,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:27",
      "text": "and Jarasia, and Eria, and Zechri, son of Iroam.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.8.28",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 28,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:28",
      "text": "These were heads of families, chiefs according to their generations: these dwelt in Jerusalem.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.8.29",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 29,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:29",
      "text": "And the father of Gabaon dwelt in Gabaon; and his wife’s name was Moacha.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.8.30",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 30,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:30",
      "text": "And her first-born son was Abdon, and Sur, and Kis, and Baal, and Nadab, and Ner,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.8.31",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 31,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:31",
      "text": "and Gedur and his brother, and Zacchur, and Makeloth.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.8.32",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 32,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:32",
      "text": "And Makeloth begot Samaa: for these dwelt in Jerusalem in the presence of their brethren with their brethren.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.8.33",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 33,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:33",
      "text": "And Ner begot Kis, and Kis begot Saul, and Saul begot Jonathan, and Melchisue, and Aminadab, and Asabal.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.8.34",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 34,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:34",
      "text": "And the son of Jonathan was Meribaal; and Meribaal begot Micha.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.8.35",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 35,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:35",
      "text": "And the sons of Micha; Phithon, and Melach, and Tharach, and Achaz.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.8.36",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 36,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:36",
      "text": "And Achaz begot Jada, and Jada begot Salaemath, and Asmoth, and Zambri; and Zambri begot Maesa;",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.8.37",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 37,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:37",
      "text": "and Maesa begot Baana: Rhaphaea was his son, Elasa his son, Esel his son.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.8.38",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 38,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:38",
      "text": "And Esel had six sons, and these were their name; Ezricam his first-born, and Ismael, and Saraia, and Abdia, and Anan, and Asa: all these were the sons of Esel.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.8.39",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 39,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:39",
      "text": "And the sons of Asel his brother; Ælam his first-born, and Jas the second, and Eliphalet the third.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.8.40",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 40,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:40",
      "text": "And the sons of Ælam were mighty men, bending the bow, and multiplying sons and grandsons, a hundred and fifty. All these were of the sons of Benjamin.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    }
  ]
}
